nodes.text: Luminara Unduli's Delta-7B Aethersprite-class light interceptor
Luminara Unduli piloted a Delta-7B Aethersprite-class light interceptor during the Clone Wars.
Luminara flew her Delta-7B during the waning years of the Clone Wars. It was painted with gray and green markings.

WizKids, Inc., before its operations were discontinued by The Topps Company, Inc., provided a sneak peek at Luminara's Delta-7B as a game piece in an expansion of the Star Wars PocketModel TCG (Trading Card Game).
